OL,3,CFilms, firsts and famous faces: What
OL,4,Cto look out for at the 2026 Oscars
OL,6,FWords by Producer Lois Smith
OL,8,FOn Sunday, the best in the film
OL,9,Fbusiness will be at the Dolby Theatre
OL,10,Fin Los Angeles for the 2026 Oscars.
OL,12,FEach year, the Hollywood ceremony
OL,13,Fcomes with glitz, glam, and great
OL,14,Fcinema, but rarely without controversy.
OL,16,FThe 98th Academy Awards will be no
OL,17,Fexception, so here is what is
OL,18,Fdifferent this year, plus what to look
OL,19,Fout for.
OL,21,FNew rules for Academy voting members
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
