OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773536630
OL,3,CFilms, firsts and famous faces: What
OL,4,Cto look out for at the 2026 Oscars
OL,6,FFor the first time, this year's
OL,7,FAcademy members must have seen all the
OL,8,Ffilms in final-round categories before
OL,9,Fcasting their ballots.
OL,11,FNew measures were introduced for 2026
OL,12,Fafter voters admitted to not having
OL,13,Fwatched all of the contenders.
OL,15,FSinners breaks records before ceremony
OL,16,Feven starts
OL,18,FSinners currently leads the way with a
OL,19,Frecord-breaking 16 nominations,
OL,20,Fopening up the opportunity for an all-
OL,21,Ftime Oscars record.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
