OL,3,CFilms, firsts and famous faces: What
OL,4,Cto look out for at the 2026 Oscars
OL,6,FThe supernatural horror film, directed
OL,7,Fby Ryan Coogler and starring Michael B
OL,8,FJordan, has already won three BAFTAs
OL,9,Fand two Golden Globes in this year's
OL,10,Fawards season.
OL,12,FSet in the Jim Crow-era south, Sinners
OL,13,Fexplores themes of racial identity,
OL,14,Freligion and the power of music.
OL,16,FAlready surpassing the bar for most
OL,17,Fnominations, if the film wins at least
OL,18,F75% of them, Sinners could smash the
OL,19,Frecord for most Oscars for a single
OL,20,Ffilm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
