OL,3,CFilms, firsts and famous faces: What
OL,4,Cto look out for at the 2026 Oscars
OL,6,FBen-Hur, Titanic, and The Lord of the
OL,7,FRings: The Return of the King are
OL,8,Fcurrently tied for the position with
OL,9,F11 awards each.
OL,11,FOne Battle After Another is also in
OL,12,Fthe battle for the coveted Best
OL,13,FPicture award.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
