OL,3,CFilms, firsts and famous faces: What
OL,4,Cto look out for at the 2026 Oscars
OL,6,FWith 13 nominations overall, the Paul
OL,7,FThomas Anderson film is centered
OL,8,Faround hostilities between
OL,9,Fundocumented immigrants and law
OL,10,Fenforcement in the United States, and,
OL,11,Falthough topical, has received
OL,12,Fcriticism over the hyper-sexualisation
OL,13,Fof black female characters.
OL,15,FAnother big award of the evening will
OL,16,Fbe Best Actress in a Leading Role, for
OL,17,Fwhich Ireland's Jessie Buckley is a
OL,18,Ffavourite to win for her performance
OL,19,Fin Hamnet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
