OL,3,CFilms, firsts and famous faces: What
OL,4,Cto look out for at the 2026 Oscars
OL,6,FMeanwhile, nominations for Best Actor
OL,7,Finclude Michael B. Jordan for Sinners,
OL,8,FLeonardo DiCaprio for One Battle After
OL,9,FAnother, and Timothee Chalamet for his
OL,10,Frole in Marty Supreme.
OL,12,FCould Timothee Chalamet's
OL,13,Fcontroversial comments cost him the
OL,14,Fwin?
OL,16,FChalamet is the youngest actor since
OL,17,FMarlon Brando to score three Oscar
OL,18,Fnominations for acting.
OL,26,@qD@TrrtD@Mrr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
