OL,3,CFilms, firsts and famous faces: What
OL,4,Cto look out for at the 2026 Oscars
OL,6,FThe French-American had been a
OL,7,Ffrontrunner to win; however, the actor
OL,8,Fis currently in hot water after
OL,9,Fcomments he made about ballet and
OL,10,Fopera last week.
OL,12,FDuring a press interview with CNN and
OL,13,FVariety, the star said: "I don't want
OL,14,Fto be working in ballet or opera where
OL,15,Fit's like, 'Hey! Keep this thing
OL,16,Falive, even though no one cares about
OL,17,Fthis anymore.'"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773536630
OL,3,CFilms, firsts and famous faces: What
OL,4,Cto look out for at the 2026 Oscars
OL,6,FRealising his misstep, he quickly
OL,7,Fadded: "All respect to all the ballet
OL,8,Fand opera people out there ... I just
OL,9,Flost 14 cents in viewership. Damn, I
OL,10,Fjust took shots for no reason."
OL,12,FAfter going viral on social media, the
OL,13,Factor's comments have sparked
OL,14,Fcriticism from audiences and
OL,15,Fperformers alike.
OL,17,FActor and comedian Whoopi Goldberg,
OL,18,FBritish opera star Camilla Kerslake,
OL,19,Fand actor Jamie Lee Curtis have all
OL,20,Fcondemned Chalamet's remarks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773536630
OL,3,CFilms, firsts and famous faces: What
OL,4,Cto look out for at the 2026 Oscars
OL,6,FSome critics have suggested that the
OL,7,Fbacklash could have cost him the win,
OL,8,Fas his best actor odds plummeted
OL,9,Fbehind Michael B Jordan.
OL,11,FIt is difficult to say whether the
OL,12,Fcontroversy will affect the outcome,
OL,13,Fas voting for the 98th annual Academy
OL,14,FAwards concluded on March 5, while the
OL,15,Foriginal video of Chalamet's comment
OL,16,Fdid not pick up in engagement until
OL,17,Faround the same time.
OL,19,FCan we expect some politically charged
OL,20,Fcomedy?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
