OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773536630
OL,3,CFilms, firsts and famous faces: What
OL,4,Cto look out for at the 2026 Oscars
OL,6,FFor a second consecutive year, Emmy
OL,7,FAward-winning television host, writer,
OL,8,Fproducer, and comedian Conan O'Brien
OL,9,Fwill return to host the Oscars.
OL,11,FOver the years, hosts have been known
OL,12,Fto make controversial jokes and
OL,13,Fpolitical jabs on stage.
OL,15,FBut last year, O'Brien stayed away
OL,16,Ffrom politics, only allowing for a
OL,17,Fquick quip aimed at US President
OL,18,FDonald Trump, without naming him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773536630
OL,3,CFilms, firsts and famous faces: What
OL,4,Cto look out for at the 2026 Oscars
OL,6,FThis year, when asked about politics
OL,7,Fand if Trump watching might factor
OL,8,Finto his show, he said: "My job is to
OL,9,Falways try and hit this very, very
OL,10,Fthin line, I think, between
OL,11,Fentertaining people and also
OL,12,Facknowledging some of the realities.
OL,14,F"So it's a dance. It's a dance that
OL,15,Fgoes on up until the show begins. I've
OL,16,Fbeen working for a really long time on
OL,17,Fmaterial for the show with my writers,
OL,18,Fand it's still evolving because we
OL,19,Flive in a very fast-paced world.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773536630
OL,3,CFilms, firsts and famous faces: What
OL,4,Cto look out for at the 2026 Oscars
OL,6,F"Jokes we thought of two months ago
OL,7,Fare irrelevant now. There might be
OL,8,Fthings that happen this week that will
OL,9,Ffind their way into the show," he
OL,10,Fadded.
OL,12,FWhat about acceptance speeches?
OL,14,FWhen it comes to speeches, a big stage
OL,15,Fis an opportunity for big statements
OL,16,Fand, subsequently, big impact.
OL,18,FOver the years, we've seen actors take
OL,19,Ftheir spotlight on stage and move it
OL,20,Fonto issues close to them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
