OL,3,CFilms, firsts and famous faces: What
OL,4,Cto look out for at the 2026 Oscars
OL,6,FLast year, the winners of Documentary
OL,7,Fof the Year, No Other Land, delivered
OL,8,Fone of the more political moments of
OL,9,Fthe evening.
OL,11,FThe documentary recorded Israel's mass
OL,12,Fexpulsion of West Bank, and was
OL,13,Fdeveloped by a Palestinian filmmaker
OL,14,Fand an Israeli journalist.
OL,16,FWhilst addressing political and social
OL,17,Fissues in acceptance speeches is by no
OL,18,Fmeans new, their effects have perhaps
OL,19,Fonly been exacerbated by social media.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
