OL,3,CFilms, firsts and famous faces: What
OL,4,Cto look out for at the 2026 Oscars
OL,6,FAt the Grammys last month, Billie
OL,7,FEilish, declaring "no one is illegal
OL,8,Fon stolen land" as she accepted her
OL,9,FSong of the Year award, went viral on
OL,10,Fsocial media.
OL,12,FThe 10-time Grammy award winner also
OL,13,Fjoined stars such as Justin Bieber,
OL,14,FSamara Joy, and Amy Allen in wearing
OL,15,F'ICE OUT' badges, protesting the
OL,16,Factions of US Immigration and Customs
OL,17,FEnforcement (ICE).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773536630
OL,3,CFilms, firsts and famous faces: What
OL,4,Cto look out for at the 2026 Oscars
OL,6,FAlso last month, ITV censored the end
OL,7,Fof Geese drummer Max Bassin's
OL,8,Facceptance speech at the BRITs, which
OL,9,Fhe concluded: "I just want to say:
OL,10,Ffree Palestine and f*** ICE."
OL,12,FAgainst an intense backdrop of
OL,13,Fgeopolitical tensions and current
OL,14,Faffairs, we may well see similar
OL,15,Fsentiments expressed on the Oscars
OL,16,Fstage.
OL,18,FIn Memoriam
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
