OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773536630
OL,3,CFilms, firsts and famous faces: What
OL,4,Cto look out for at the 2026 Oscars
OL,6,FThe 2026 'In Memoriam' segment will
OL,7,Fhonour more legends than in previous
OL,8,Fyears, with the Academy airing an
OL,9,Fextended version.
OL,11,FThey are expected to pay tribute to
OL,12,FHollywood titans who passed in the
OL,13,Flast year, such as Diane Keaton,
OL,14,FCatherine O'Hara and Robert Redford.
OL,16,FO'Brien has also confirmed there will
OL,17,Fbe a special tribute to director Rob
OL,18,FReiner.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31217
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773536630
OL,3,CFilms, firsts and famous faces: What
OL,4,Cto look out for at the 2026 Oscars
OL,6,FReiner, who directed classics such as
OL,7,FThis Is Spinal Tap, The Princess Bride
OL,8,Fand When Harry Met Sally, was killed
OL,9,Falongside his wife, producer and
OL,10,Fphotographer, Michele Singer in
OL,11,FDecember.
OL,13,FWho will be performing?
OL,15,FIn a controversial move from the
OL,16,FAcademy, just two of the nominees in
OL,17,Fthe Best Original Song category will
OL,18,Fbe performed live.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31218
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773536630
OL,3,CFilms, firsts and famous faces: What
OL,4,Cto look out for at the 2026 Oscars
OL,6,FThe performances will be inspired by
OL,7,FSinners (I Lied to You) and KPop Demon
OL,8,FHunters (Golden).
OL,10,FKPop Demon Hunters is up for two
OL,11,FOscars: Best Animated Feature and Best
OL,12,FOriginal Song, and has proved to be a
OL,13,Fcultural sensation.
OL,15,FLast year, producers broke an 80-year-
OL,16,Fold tradition by scrapping live
OL,17,Fperformances of some Original Song
OL,18,Fnominees.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/20
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
