PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1773536630
OL,3,CFilms, firsts and famous faces: What
OL,4,Cto look out for at the 2026 Oscars
OL,6,FThis year, organisers have assured
OL,7,Fthat every song "will be introduced
OL,8,Fthrough a bespoke package built from
OL,9,Ffootage of the film it was written
OL,10,Ffor, grounding the song firmly in its
OL,11,Fcinematic purpose."
OL,13,FThey added: "Where appropriate, these
OL,14,Fpackages may also include select
OL,15,Fbehind-the-scenes elements that offer
OL,16,Finsight into the songwriting process
OL,17,Fand creative intent."
OL,19,FYou can watch the 98th Academy Awards
OL,20,Flive on ITV1 and ITVX from 10.15pm on
OL,21,FSunday, March 15.
